          <td style="white-space:nowrap">Milestone
            
            <a name="research-subject-state-type-Milestone"> </a>
          
          </td>
          
          <td>Milestone status</td>
          
          <td>One of a set of milestone events that once they have occurred remain true thereafter.  For example once a subject has reached the &quot;Signed Informed Consent&quot; milestone they achieve a status of &quot;Consented&quot; that will be true thereafter, even when they have left the study.  For a subject a number of these states can be simulataneously true and should be recorded.</td>
        
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          
          <td style="white-space:nowrap">Enrollment
            
            <a name="research-subject-state-type-Enrollment"> </a>
          
          </td>
          
          <td>Enrollment status</td>
          
          <td>This is a status that can only have a single value at a given point in time.  The subject is either on-study or off-study.</td>
        
        </tr>
      
